## 4. API Response Format

### Success Response
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "data": { ... },
    "message": "Operation completed"
}
```

### Error Response
```json
{
    "success": false,
    "error": {
        "code": "ERROR_CODE",
        "message": "Human readable message"
    }
}
```

